## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-102">Экземпляр <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs> создается, когда <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> или <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> объекта вызывает `AudioSignalProblemOccurred` событий.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-102">An instance of <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs> is created when the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine> or <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer> object raises an `AudioSignalProblemOccurred` event.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-103">Чтобы получить сведения, относящиеся к `AudioSignalProblemOccurred` событий, доступ к следующие свойства в обработчик для события:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-103">To obtain information related to an `AudioSignalProblemOccurred` event, access the following properties in the handler for the event:</span></span>  

-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioLevel%2A>  

-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioPosition%2A>  

-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioSignalProblem%2A>  

-   <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.RecognizerAudioPosition%2A>  

 <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-104"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioPosition%2A> Свойство ссылается на позицию устройство ввода в созданный аудиопотока.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-104">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioPosition%2A> property references the input device's position in its generated audio stream.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-105">В отличие от этого <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.RecognizerAudioPosition%2A> свойство ссылается на позицию распознавателя внутри его аудио входных данных.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-105">By contrast, the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.RecognizerAudioPosition%2A> property references the recognizer's position within its audio input.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-106">Эти позиции могут быть разными.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-106">These positions can be different.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-107">Дополнительные сведения см. в разделе [с помощью событий распознавания речи](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01c598ca-2e0e-4e89-b303-cd1cef9e8482).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-107">For more information, see [Using Speech Recognition Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/01c598ca-2e0e-4e89-b303-cd1cef9e8482).</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-108"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioSignalProblem%2A> Свойство указывает, какие проблемы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-108">The <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs.AudioSignalProblem%2A> property indicates which problem occurred.</span></span>  

 <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-109">Интерфейс <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs> является производным от интерфейса <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-109"><xref:System.Speech.Recognition.AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs> derives from <xref:System.EventArgs>.</span></span>  



## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="02c6d-110">В следующем примере определяется обработчик событий, собирает информацию о <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioSignalProblemOccurred> событий.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="02c6d-110">The following example defines an event handler that gathers information about an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.AudioSignalProblemOccurred> event.</span></span>  

```csharp  

private SpeechRecognitionEngine sre;  

// Initialize the speech recognition engine.  
private void Initialize()  
{  
  sre = new SpeechRecognitionEngine();  

  // Add a handler for the AudioSignalProblemOccurred event.  
  sre.AudioSignalProblemOccurred += new EventHandler<AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs>(sre_AudioSignalProblemOccurred);  
}  

// Gather information when the AudioSignalProblemOccurred event is raised.  
void sre_AudioSignalProblemOccurred(object sender, AudioSignalProblemOccurredEventArgs e)  
{  
  StringBuilder details = new StringBuilder();  

  details.AppendLine("Audio signal problem information:");  
  details.AppendFormat(  
    " Audio level:               {0}" + Environment.NewLine +  
    " Audio position:            {1}" + Environment.NewLine +  
    " Audio signal problem:      {2}" + Environment.NewLine +  
    " Recognition engine audio position: {3}" + Environment.NewLine,  
    e.AudioLevel, e.AudioPosition,  e.AudioSignalProblem,  
    e.RecognizerAudioPosition);  

  // Insert additional event handler code here.  
}  

```
